<i>noun</i>: 한탄 [한ː탄], 통곡 [통ː곡], 탄식 [탄ː식], 탄성 [탄ː성], 애통 [애통], 애석 [애석], 개탄 [개ː탄] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>한탄 [한ː탄]</dt><br>
<dd>lamentation; deploration</dd><br>
<dd>분하고 억울한 일을 당했을 때나 자신의 잘못을 깨달았을 때 한숨을 쉬며 탄식함. 또는 그 한숨.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of letting out a sigh and grieving when facing an unfair and vexing event or realizing one's own fault; or such a sigh.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>통곡 [통ː곡]</dt><br>
<dd>lamentation; weeping bitterly</dd><br>
<dd>큰 소리로 슬피 욺.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of crying sadly and loudly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탄식 [탄ː식]</dt><br>
<dd>lamentation; sigh</dd><br>
<dd>슬프거나 힘든 일이 있을 때 심하게 한숨을 쉼. 또는 그 한숨.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making a deep sigh, as one is sad or troubled, or such a sigh.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>탄성 [탄ː성]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lamentation; sigh</dd><br>
<dd>슬프거나 힘든 일이 있을 때 심하게 한숨을 쉬며 내는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>The sound of a deep sigh made when one is sad or troubled.</dd><br>
<dd>2. exclamation</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 감탄하는 소리.</dd><br>
<dd>A sound of great admiration.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>애통 [애통]</dt><br>
<dd>grief; lamentation; deploration</dd><br>
<dd>슬퍼하고 마음 아파함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of feeling sad and heartbroken.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>애석 [애석]</dt><br>
<dd>grief; lamentation; regret</dd><br>
<dd>슬프고 안타까움.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of feeling sad and pitiful.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>개탄 [개ː탄]</dt><br>
<dd>lamentation; deploring</dd><br>
<dd>분하거나 안타깝게 여겨 탄식함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of moaning out of anger or regret.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>